        "cooked": "<p>The Parametric Model Maker is rotating the model for some reason even it fits on a Build Plate. Tested on H2D and P1S. Both can print 200x100mm objects.</p>\n<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/original/3X/9/5/95f0c667b9cf379f5439d422959aaf348a3d60d0.png\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/lor04BFvQQ1bsJQLZBsgGVQjbaM.png?dl=1\" title=\"image\"><img src=\"https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/9/5/95f0c667b9cf379f5439d422959aaf348a3d60d0_2_690x325.png\" alt=\"image\" data-base62-sha1=\"lor04BFvQQ1bsJQLZBsgGVQjbaM\" width=\"690\" height=\"325\" srcset=\"https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/9/5/95f0c667b9cf379f5439d422959aaf348a3d60d0_2_690x325.png, https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/9/5/95f0c667b9cf379f5439d422959aaf348a3d60d0_2_1035x487.png 1.5x, https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/9/5/95f0c667b9cf379f5439d422959aaf348a3d60d0_2_1380x650.png 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"B4B3AB\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">image</span><span class=\"informations\">2623\u00d71238 242 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>Can be validated on this model:</p><aside class=\"onebox allowlistedgeneric\" data-onebox-src=\"https://makerworld.com/en/models/103266-organizer-box\">\n  <header class=\"source\">\n      <img src=\"https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/original/3X/1/c/1c24b83c1500163989015ea75cfe140f0b31d275.png\" class=\"site-icon\" data-dominant-color=\"B1B1B1\" width=\"400\" height=\"400\">\n\n      <a href=\"https://makerworld.com/en/models/103266-organizer-box\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">makerworld.com</a>\n  </header>\n\n  <article class=\"onebox-body\">\n    <div class=\"aspect-image\" style=\"--aspect-ratio:690/414;\"><img src=\"https://cdn-forum.bambulab.com/optimized/3X/d/4/d4db054c7eda37ce6e955adfeeba442d4be91270_2_666x500.jpeg\" class=\"thumbnail\" data-dominant-color=\"A28A73\" width=\"666\" height=\"500\"></div>\n\n<h3><a href=\"https://makerworld.com/en/models/103266-organizer-box\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">Organizer Box by Benjamin Kott MakerWorld: Download Free 3D Models</a></h3>\n\n  <p>Organizer Box (Fully Parameterized) with Fusion 360 Source Files and Parametric Model Maker support.Use the available print profiles if you want to have a specific size, if you are more into tinkering fetch the Fusion 360 file and enjoy all the...</p>\n\n\n  </article>\n\n  <div class=\"onebox-metadata\">\n    \n    \n  </div>\n\n  <div style=\"clear: both\"></div>\n</aside>\n\n<p>Use Settings:<br>\nLength: 200<br>\nWidth: 100</p>",
